## Day 2 of SQL Advent Calendar

### Today's Question:
Santa wants to know which gifts weigh more than 1 kg. Can you list them?

### Table Name: `gifts`

| gift_name    | recipient | weight_kg |
|--------------|-----------|-----------|
| Toy Train    | John      | 2.5       |
| Chocolate Box| Alice     | 0.8       |
| Teddy Bear   | Sophia    | 1.2       |
| Board Game   | Liam      | 0.9       |

---

### Solution:

```sql
SELECT 
    gift_name
FROM 
    gifts
WHERE 
    weight_kg > 1;
```
